of water there.

00:18:10.750 --> 00:18:12.260
And you're keeping track
of one variable in

00:18:12.260 --> 00:18:13.300
terms of the other.

00:18:13.300 --> 00:18:16.360
And the relationship will always
be a chain rule type of

00:18:16.360 --> 00:18:17.140
relationship.

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:19.110
So, therefore, you'll be able to
- if you know one you'll be

00:18:19.110 --> 00:18:20.810
able to figure out the other.

00:18:20.810 --> 00:18:22.890
Provided you get all of
the related rates.

00:18:22.890 --> 00:18:24.530
These are what are called
related rates.

00:18:24.530 --> 00:18:26.010
This is a rate of something
with respect to

00:18:26.010 --> 00:18:28.050
something, etc. etc.

00:18:28.050 --> 00:18:30.540
So it's really all about
