00:21:24.040 --> 00:21:27.410
OK, so here's the situation.

00:21:27.410 --> 00:21:29.860
We have a problem.

00:21:29.860 --> 00:21:33.170
And we've hung a string.

00:21:33.170 --> 00:21:39.630
And it went down like this and
